OL,3,CJersey Election 2026: Your questions
OL,4,Canswered
OL,6,FJersey's election will take place this
OL,7,FSunday (7 June), with 92 candidates on
OL,8,Fvarious ballots across all 12 parishes.
OL,10,FPolling will take place on a weekend
OL,11,Ffor the first time and rules have been
OL,12,Frelaxed in a bid to increase turnout.
OL,14,FAll eligible voters are automatically
OL,15,Fregistered and you can check your
OL,16,Fstatus at vote.je.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
