OL,3,CJersey Election 2026: Your questions
OL,4,Canswered
OL,6,FSenators are also returning after
OL,7,Fbeing scrapped in 2022. The hope is
OL,8,Fthat the Assembly will benefit from
OL,9,Fhaving some members with an "island-
OL,10,Fwide mandate".
OL,12,FThere will be 49 members elected to
OL,13,Fthe States Assembly. That includes
OL,14,Fnine Senators, 12 Connetables
OL,15,F(Constables), and 37 Deputies, who
OL,16,Fwill each represent one of nine
OL,17,Felectoral constituencies.
OL,26,@vD@Wrr
