OL,3,CJersey Election 2026: Your questions
OL,4,Canswered
OL,6,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,7,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,8,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,9,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,10,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,11,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,12,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX and YouTube,
OL,13,Fwith new episodes each Thursday...
OL,15,FWhere can I vote?
OL,17,FWhere you vote depends on where you
OL,18,Flive. Normally, it will be in your
OL,19,Fparish hall but sites vary. The full
OL,20,Flist is available online at vote.je.
OL,21,FVoting starts at 8am and ends at 8pm.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
