OL,3,CJersey Election 2026: Your questions
OL,4,Canswered
OL,6,FWho am I voting for?
OL,8,FThis year, islanders will elect
OL,9,Fpoliticians to three distinct roles:
OL,11,F1. Senators - they represent the whole
OL,12,Fisland.
OL,14,F2. Constables - they represent a
OL,15,Fsingle parish, set rates in the Parish
OL,16,FAssembly, and preside over the Roads
OL,17,FCommittee.
OL,19,F3. Deputies - they represent your
OL,20,Flocal district, appoint the Government
OL,21,Fof Jersey, and hold it to account.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
