OL,3,CJersey Election 2026: Your questions
OL,4,Canswered
OL,6,FYou can find a full list of candidates
OL,7,Fhere.
OL,9,FWhat should I bring?
OL,11,FJust like in the UK, you will need to
OL,12,Fbring voter ID to the polls. That can
OL,13,Fbe a passport, a driving license, a
OL,14,Fwork pass, your YOTI account or a
OL,15,Futility bill.
OL,17,FWhat happens next?
OL,19,FResults from across the island will be
OL,20,Fannounced throughout Sunday night once
OL,21,Fpolls close at 8pm.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
