OL,3,CJersey Election 2026: Your questions
OL,4,Canswered
OL,6,FThe full picture is likely to emerge
OL,7,Fby Monday morning and you can stay
OL,8,Facross the counts as they happen on
OL,9,Fthe ITV Channel website.
OL,11,FSuccessful candidates will be sworn in
OL,12,Fon Friday 12 June and then the States
OL,13,FAssembly will have a week to consider
OL,14,Fthe new Chief Minister.
OL,16,FAnyone seeking the top job will give a
OL,17,Fspeech outlining their vision and then
OL,18,Fface up to one hour of questions from
OL,19,Fother Members of the Assembly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
