OL,3,CJersey Election 2026: Your questions
OL,4,Canswered
OL,6,FA vote will then be held - if no
OL,7,Fcandidate secures a majority in the
OL,8,Ffirst round, the person with the
OL,9,Ffewest number of votes will be
OL,10,Feliminated and the process will be
OL,11,Frepeated until a winner is found.
OL,13,FThe new Chief Minister will then
OL,14,Fchoose their ministerial nominations,
OL,15,Fwhich will be debated by States
OL,16,FMembers.
OL,18,FThe first "standard meeting" of the
OL,19,Fnew Assembly will be held on Tuesday
OL,20,F14 July.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
